Package: scVeloR
Type: Package
Title: RNA Velocity Analysis for Single-Cell RNA-Seq Data
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-01-25
Authors@R: c(
    person("Zaoqu", "Liu", 
           email = "liuzaoqu@163.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0000-0000")))
Description: A comprehensive R implementation of RNA velocity analysis for 
    single-cell RNA sequencing data. This package provides methods for 
    estimating RNA velocities using steady-state, stochastic, and dynamical 
    models. It includes functions for velocity graph construction, embedding 
    projection, transition matrix computation, and various visualization tools.
    The package is optimized for performance using Rcpp and supports parallel 
    computation via the future framework. Compatible with Seurat V4 and V5 objects.
